Jamie Lee Curtis, 64, showed off her figure as she took to the red carpet in a sparkly dark blue gown with a plunging neckline. The dress featured gathering detail just below her chest, extenuating her ample assets. She styled the show-stopping number with a pair of black heels while styling her signature silver locks in a short pixie style. Jamie accessorised with a pendant necklace and showed off her ageless complexion with her simple yet elegant makeup style. The Hollywood star attended the 34th Producers Guild Awards to present an award, while her film, Everything Everywhere All At Once, won big at the ceremony.